{"tid":2079663,"cid":37,"subCid":13,"title":"45呎房 雙人床 想有個位放電腦椅用電腦 有冇計","createTime":"2020-06-26T02:36:50.000Z","updateTime":"2020-06-27T02:57:15.000Z","uid":107400,"like":7,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":12,"replies":[{"pid":"83fd7d5b8244ad3e17cb49268c35d5cb00dd6fbb","tid":2079663,"uid":107400,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-06-26T02:36:50.000Z","msg":"頭先開錯 試吓開返係裝修台先<br />\n<br />\n間房2m x 2.2m左右<br />\n<br />\n放完張雙人床已經冇左大半<img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/Uh9jGfL.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FUh9jGfL.png&h=c9ade179&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n想有個位用下電腦 但唔想坐係床上用<br />\n<br />\n另外都想放到個衣櫃<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n上網睇最合適係組合床<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/G63AeCy.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FG63AeCy.jpg&h=c1e9838d&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n但一諗起每日要上上落落就冇曬mood<br />\n每日返工咁辛苦 <br />\n放工正常都想沖完涼達落床攤唞下<br />\n放假坐係張正正常常嘅電腦椅上打下機<br />\n<br />\n香港人前世做錯咗啲乜<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n暫時見到有啲有轆電腦枱可能啱用 但仲未諗到點用<br />\n有冇高手分享下經驗"},{"pid":"b20f9ce957e3b13e90bbef3d11264baec72fff4c","tid":2079663,"uid":129348,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-06-26T02:38:38.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/2OiTLO9.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F2OiTLO9.jpg&h=e748ebce&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://na.cx/i/XTO8zHv.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FXTO8zHv.jpg&h=b69f9215&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://na.cx/i/zYyHD9a.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FzYyHD9a.jpg&h=3f13d226&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n【#71遊行 堅持五大訴求 反抗國安惡法】<br />\n<br />\n日期｜2020 年 7 月 1 日 星期三<br />\n集合地點｜維園集合<br />\n集合時間｜2PM<br />\n起步時間｜3PM<br />\n遊行終點｜金鐘添美道<br />\n*遊行正申請不反對通知書"},{"pid":"43b501682dc3131843b632594772ea57b10cc553","tid":2079663,"uid":28159,"like":1,"d